abstract: LATROBE, Pa., June 7 (AP) -- Home remedies for various miseries are as common as apple pie, but few people have received as many in recent months as Arnold Palmer, the millionaire golfing idol stricken with a sore hip, the putting yips and a bad tournament slump.
headline_main: Palmer, Swamped by Remedies From His Army, Has Own Plan to Cure Slump
headline_print_headline: Palmer, Swamped by Remedies From His Army, Has Own Plan to Cure Slump
